'''Rosewings''' were [[Insect/Legends|insects]] that emerged from their pupae in spring, transformed from [[peggelar]]s. [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] collected the discarded pupae as a child on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]].

